                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9124" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">EPSM-1015</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1380 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">科技赋能，创新驱动：陕建集团引领行业高质量发展</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Technology Empowers, Innovation Drives: Shanxi Construction Group Leads the Industry&#39;s High-Quality Development</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">董雪艳，李芙英，黄远宏，龚汨嘉，李希熙，王铁男，李宁</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">西北工业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">陕西建工集团股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">建筑、建材业与房地产业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">科技发展部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">13 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">国有企业；陕西集团；科技创新；自主研发；产学研合作；2024百优案例；国企专项</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">State-owned enterprises, Shaanxi Construction Engineering Group Corporation Limited, scientific and technological innovation, independent R&amp;D, industry-academia- research cooperation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">科技创新是企业降本增效、提高竞争力的关键途径，是社会经济增长的首要驱动力，亦是反映国家综合国力和国际地位的核心因素。国有企业的科技创新机制是中国特色社会主义市场经济的重要体现，关系到我国的经济稳定和长远发展。科技创新相关知识点的学习能够帮助学员提升其企业管理能力、战略决策能力、技术创新能力，亦能增强其民族自信心和科技自强决心。本案例描述了陕建集团在发展的各阶段不断进行科技创新，引领我国建筑行业高质量发展的故事情节。通过案例学习，引导学员了解并掌握企业进行科技创新的动因、科技创新的过程和效果、科技创新所需的资源基础，以及归纳中国特色的科技创新模式等重要内容，培养学员逻辑思维能力、归纳总结能力、独立思考能力、团队沟通能力、批判思维能力等，激发其对创新驱动发展战略的深度思考，提升学员科技强国、实现高水平科技自立自强的使命担当精神。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Scientific and technological innovation is a key way for enterprises to reduce costs, increase efficiency and improve competitiveness. It is the primary driving force for social and economic growth, and a core factor reflecting a country’s comprehensive national strength and international status. The science and technology innovation mechanism of state-owned enterprises is an important embodiment of the socialist market economy with Chinese characteristics, which is related to China’s economic stability and long-term development. The study of science and technology innovation can help students to improve their enterprise management ability, strategic decision-making ability, technological innovation ability, and also enhance their national self-confidence and determination of scientific and technological self-improvement. This case describes the storyline of Shaanxi Construction Engineering Group Corporation Limited (SCEGCL), which has led the high-quality development of China’s construction industry by continuously carrying out scientific and technological innovation at various stages of development. Through the case study, participants are guided to understand and master the motivation of enterprises to carry out scientific and technological innovation, the process and effect of scientific and technological innovation, the resource base required for scientific and technological innovation, and the scientific and technological innovation model with Chinese characteristics, etc., and cultivate the participants’ ability to think logically, summarize, think independently, communicate with the team, and think critically. It can also stimulate in-depth thinking about the innovation-driven development strategy and enhance the participants’ spirit of mission and responsibility to strengthen the country with science and technology and to achieve a high level of scientific and technological self-reliance and self-improvement.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《创新管理》、《战略管理》、《管理学》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">科技创新；科技创新的活动与模式</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-01</td>
                            </tr>
